                <project id="10591" key="JCR">Jackrabbit Content Repository</project>
                        <description>Both &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-1310&quot; title=&quot;Webdav: Drop xerces dependency&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;JCR-1310&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-1343&quot; title=&quot;Replace xerces for serialization by JAXP&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;JCR-1343&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt; need XML serialization functionality and we&amp;#39;ve also previously (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-367&quot; title=&quot;Remove dependency on Xerces&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;JCR-367&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-1086&quot; title=&quot;JCR2SPI: Workspace.getImportHandler creates a handler which doesn&amp;#39;t work properly under JDK 1.4.&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;JCR-1086&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) implemented something similar.&lt;br/&gt;
